Name: Elbub
About the game: Relaxing and simple short game about flying in abstract, peaceful environment. Play as a bubble, follow the coloured tape to reach the main bubble. Key Features: Unique calming, peaceful game. Abstract and colourful gaming environment. Relaxing sound atmosphere. Simple and intuitive gaming experience. Alternative psychedelic display mode. No stories, just flying and lots of bubbles!
